And remind them to buckle up before driving.
Above all, the campaign wants to appeal to the consciences of young drivers, motorcyclists, pedestrians and, last but not least, professional drivers.
And what is shown in the spots?
Especially stories of people that appeal to emotions.
The &quot;bloody&quot; slogan of the whole campaign also bears witness to this:
