Another &quot;mistake&quot; was made by the forgers at HIB Kft. from Nyíregyháza: This company was in the process of being dissolved at the time (2001) when the Fiatal Városért Egyesület group is said to have eaten there - the liquidator consequently stated that not having issued the invoices themselves.
Deliberately fake
