In the period from October to December 2005, this company is said to have issued several invoices for the sale of computer components with a total value of around HUF 18 million.
According to the investigating authority, Cash Investment Kft. from Kiskunhalas, which has been in liquidation since September 14, 2005, is said to have acted as the purchaser of these invoices.
